params.name: config
params.description: Model configuration class with all the parameters of the model.Initializing with a config file does not load the weights associated with the model, only theconfiguration. Check out the from_pretrained() method to load the model weights.

params.name: image_codebook
params.description: If passed, the image codebook will be set to this. Otherwise. it willbe initialized using the image_codebook_config defined in the config first as the first parameter.
